text: The area of Urakawa District in Hidaka Subprefecture. is a district located in Hidaka Subprefecture, Hokkaido, Japan. As of 2004, the district has an estimated population of 15,986 and a density of 23.03 persons per km². The total area is 694.23 km². ==Towns and villages== *Urakawa Category:Districts in Hokkaido
title: Urakawa District, Hokkaido
